From 2a60dc6f5265f2391759711ef14d91e1c22e9b49 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 15:59:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ci: add upload-artifact step to build-apk workflow

The build-apk workflow was building APK successfully but NOT uploading
it as an artifact, so users couldn't download the APK from GitHub Actions.

Added 'Upload APK Artifact' step using actions/upload-artifact@v4:
- Name: GameMapperMind-debug-apk
- Path: android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
- Retention: 30 days
- if-no-files-found: error (fail build if APK missing)

After this fix, successful builds will have downloadable APK artifact.
---
 .github/workflows/build-apk.yml | 8 ++++++++
 1 file changed, 8 insertions(+)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/build-apk.yml b/.github/workflows/build-apk.yml
index bae9ea2..78d5578 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/build-apk.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/build-apk.yml
@@ -46,3 +46,11 @@ jobs:
       - name: Build APK
         working-directory: ./android
         run: ./gradlew assembleDebug
+
+      - name: Upload APK Artifact
+        uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
+        with:
+          name: GameMapperMind-debug-apk
+          path: android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk
+          retention-days: 30
+          if-no-files-found: error
-- 
2.47.3

